title: United Kingdom Imports - Vehicles Not Railway, Tram, Parts & Accessories
description: Imports - Vehicles Not Railway, Tram, Parts & Accessories in the United Kingdom increased to 4821.06 GBP Million in September from 4024.59 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Vehicles Not Railway, Tram, Parts & Acce in the United Kingdom averaged 3365.86 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 6305.14 GBP Million in March of 2019 and a record low of 1168.94 GBP Million in April of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Vehicles Not Railway, Tram, Parts & Ac.
